"&#xa0;\nWritten evidence submitted by Girlguiding (WSC075)&#xa0;\nAbout Girlguiding\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;The Girls’ Attitudes Survey\nGirlguiding’s submission focuses \non evidence from the Girls’ Attitudes Surveys, our annual research into the opinions of girls and young women throughout the UK aged 11-21, described below (points 4-6). This evidence pr\novides unique insight into why young women’s interest in STEM subjects may drop off. Girlguiding’s youth programmes offer a good practice example of how girls’ and young women’s interest in STEM subjects can be encouraged (points 21-22).\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nScience and \nEngineering\n&#xa0;\nGender bias in careers\n&#xa0;&#xa0;\n&#xa0;&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;Role models\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nEducation and \nCareers\n&#xa0;&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nSTEM subjects in Girlguid\ni\nng’s youth programmes\n&#xa0;Girlguiding’s programme for girls and young \nwomen includes activities and resources that challenge the gender stereotypes that our evidence shows influence girls\n’\n decisions about subject choice and career aspirations. \nIt also includes specific focus on STEM subjects. \n&#xa0;&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nSeptember 2013\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nAppendix&#xa0;Selected questions&#xa0;\nTitle: Do you think these areas of activity are more for men, more for women, or both equally? \n–\n Engineering\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n              \n              \n              \n              \n              \n              \n              \n              \n              \n              \n              \n              \n              \n              \n&#xa0;\nTitle: Do you think these areas of activity are more for men, more for women, or both equally? \n–\n Science\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nTitle: Do you think these areas of activity are more for men, more for women, or both equally? - Global warming and environment issues\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n See the videos here: http://www.girlguiding.org.uk/our_research/real_role_models/meet_our_real_role_models.aspx\n \nhttp://www.girlguiding.org.uk/brownies/badges/computer.asp\nhttp://www.girlguiding.org.uk/brownies/badges/numberfun.asp\nhttp://www.girlguiding.org.uk/brownies/badges/science.asp\nhttp://www.girlguiding.org.uk/brownies/badges/stargazer.asp\n \nhttp://www.girlguiding.org.uk/Guides/gfibadge/gfi/beconstructive.html\nhttp://www.girlguiding.org.uk/Guides/gfibadge/gfi/experiment.html\nhttp://www.girlguiding.org.uk/Guides/gfibadge/gfi/space.html\n"